==Notable person==
*Chavit Singson, ex-politician, businessman.
*Floro Crisologo, lawyer, politician.
*Vincent Crisologo, ex-politician.
*Rogelio Singson, ex-politician and former cabinet member.
*Marcelino Crisólogo, politician, poet, writer and playwright. &quot;Calle Crisologo&quot; or &quot;Mena Crisologo Street&quot; was named after him.
*Isabelo de los Reyes, patriot, politician, writer, journalist, and labor activist.
*Leona Florentino, poet, dramatist, and playwright; recognized as the &quot;mother of Philippine women&#x27;s literature&quot;.
* Bryan Quitoriano, radio broadcaster
*Deogracias Victor B. Savellano, former governor, former Vice Governor, former House of Representatives Undersecretary for Livestock at the Department of Agriculture and former Mayor of Cabugao

